(Learning Objectives) Tj
T*
(- Explain the meaning of CSS in Computer Science using accurate subject vocabulary.) Tj
T*
(- Describe the key ideas behind selectors, properties, spacing, colors, and layout.) Tj
T*
(- Apply CSS to examples such as styling a page with classes and simple layout rules.) Tj
T*
